(0000000387, 0000000025, 0000000003, 0000000001, '# SelfHelp WebApp Documentation\r\n\r\nThis demo page serves the purpose of documenting the SelfHelp WebApp.\r\nUse [this tutorial](!%tutorial.pdf) as a guide for some first steps to create a new WebApp.\r\nFurther, the page includes a demonstration of available [styles](#styles), provides information about the [server configuration](#configs), and gives some hints as to how the app can be [extended programatically](#extend).\r\n\r\nThe complete documentation of the source code is accessible [here](!https://selfhelp.psy.unibe.ch/demo/doc/doxygen/html/index.html).'),
